      <title>内塔尼亚胡访问联合国，从战争走向外交敌对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前，本雅明·内塔尼亚胡来到联合国，宣扬阿拉伯世界和平的祝福。他回来时，该地区正处于全面战争的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/israel-s-netanyahu-flies-from-war-to-diplomatic-hostility-with-un-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
